e N+1, then reverse, the array goes from oldest to newest. `messages[0]` would b
e the oldest message\'s sequence_id. For pagination, the next cursor should be t
he oldest message in the current page so the next query can get messages with se
quence_id < cursor.\n\nLet me trace through:\n- Query DESC by sequence_id, take 
21\n- results = [msg20, msg19, ..., msg1, msg0] (newest first)\n- hasMore = resu
