t load without cursor, we get the MOST RECENT 20 messages. If there are 50 messa
ges total (seq 1-50), first load gets seq 50 down to 31. After reverse: [31, 32,
..., 50]. The nextCursor = 31. Next query: sequence_id < 31 gets seq 30 down to 
