s` with no limit. This is the Major issue I identified.\n\n7. Looking at `im_blo
c.dart` `_onSetCurrentConversation`:\n```dart\nif (event.conversationId != null 
&&\n    _pendingMessages.containsKey(event.conversationId) &&\n    state is Mess
agesLoaded) {\n```\nWhat if `state is MessageSending` or `MessageSent` when swit
ching conversations? Then pending messages are NOT merged. But switching convers
ations typically happens from the list page where the state is likely `Conversat
ionListLoaded` or `ImInitial`, not `MessagesLoaded`. When you tap a conversation
, `ChatPage` calls `ImSetCurrentConversation` and `LoadMessages`. `LoadMessages`
