his is fine.\n\nWhat about `im_bloc.dart` `_pendingMessages` unlimited growth? T
he spec says:\n"BLoC 中所有 `List`、`Map` 缓存必须设置合理上限；超出上限时从尾部
或头部淘汰"\n\nThis is a clear violation. In an IM app, if the user receives mes
sages from many conversations while not viewing them, `_pendingMessages` can gro
w unbounded, leading to OOM. This is a Major issue.\n\nWhat about the disconnect
bug where `MessageSending` state doesn\'t transition on disconnect? If a user se
nds a message and the socket drops before ack, the message is stuck in "sending"
state indefinitely. The user cannot retry because retry only shows for `failed` 
