age(...);\n} else {\n  // mark as failed\n}\n```\n\nThe `isConnected` is checked
at send time. So if the socket is disconnected when the user hits send, the mess
age is marked `failed`. Good.\n\nBut if the socket IS connected at send time, an
d THEN disconnects before ack, the message stays in `MessageSending`. This is th
e edge case.\n\nAlso, when the socket unexpectedly disconnects, the BLoC state s
