tches this and creates the system message. But `createSystemMessage` doesn\'t up
date `conversationRepo.update({updated_at: new Date()})`. This means the convers
ation list ordering might not put newly matched conversations at the top!\n\nWai
t, looking at `matching.service.ts`, when a match is created, it already creates
the conversation. Let me check if it sets `updated_at` there. But regardless, `c
reateSystemMessage` doesn\'t update `conversation.updated_at`. So the conversati
