indings.\n\n**Major Issues:**\n\n1. **ImBloc `_pendingMessages` lacks cache limi
t** - Violates Flutter spec "BLoC 中所有 `List`、`Map` 缓存必须设置合理上限". Ca
n cause OOM.\n\n2. **Socket disconnect state not propagated to ImBloc** - `ImSoc
ketClient` has no `onDisconnect`/`onReconnect` callbacks. `ImBloc` cannot update
